Interface OpenSet

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OpenSetAsPriorityQueue, OpenSetAsPriorityQueueFastContains, OpenSetAsPriorityQueueFastContainsFastReplace, OpenSetImpl

    public interface OpenSet
    Common interface for containers with open states.
    Author:
    Przemysław Klęsk (wi.zut.edu.pl), Marcin Korzeń (wi.zut.edu.pl)
